310
00:22:41,216 --> 00:22:42,550
Bueno, está bien.

311
00:22:43,134 --> 00:22:44,144
Está bien.

312
00:22:44,344 --> 00:22:45,345
No es falso.

313
00:22:48,098 --> 00:22:49,808
