00:29:34,504 --> 00:29:35,639
<i>Y comenzamos.</i>

420
00:29:35,839 --> 00:29:37,349
<i>Se siente la emoción</i>

421
00:29:37,549 --> 00:29:40,769
<i>en el famoso Sportatorium,
