438
00:30:25,138 --> 00:30:27,399
<i>Le da un gran golpe en el torso.</i>

439
00:30:27,599 --> 00:30:29,317
<i>Lo deja sin aliento.</i>

440
00:30:29,517 --> 00:30:30,736
